ht Outta Oz' With A Semi-Unnecessary Deluxe Edit |last1=Brown |first1=Jonathan |last2= |first2= |date=March 22, 2017 |website=[[Inquisitr]] | publisher = |access-date=October 25, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2017\n| \"[[Power (Little Mix song)|Power]]\"\n| [[Little Mix]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newnownext.com/willam-alaska-courtney-little-mix-power/06/2017/|title=Alaska, Courtney Act, Willam Will Have The \"Power\" In New Little Mix Video|work=NewNowNext|accessdate=6 June 2017|date=6 June 2017|last=Salandra|first=Anam}}</ref>\n|-\n|2018\n|\"Girly\"\n|John Duff\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/john-duff-girly-video_us_5b981cade4b0511db3e6d46a |title=In 'Girly,' Singer John Duff Strikes Pop Diva Poses To Challenge Gender Norms |last1=Wong |first1=Curtis M. |last2= |first2= |date=September 12, 2018 |website=[[HuffPost]] | publisher =[[Oath Inc.]] |access-date=October 25, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|2019\n|\"Star Maps\"\n|[[Aly & AJ]]\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ew.com/music/2019/06/12/aly-aj-star-maps-music-video/ |title=Watch Aly & AJ's 'Star Maps' music video featuring stars from Shameless, Drag Race, Silicon Valley, The Goldbergs, and more |last1=Huff |first1=Lauren |last2= |first2= |date=June 12, 2019 |website=[[Entertainment Weekly]] | publisher = |access-date=June 12, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==Discography==\n''See also: [[DWV (group)#discography]] and [[The AAA Girls#discography]]''\n===Albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:14em;\"| Title\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:19em;\"| Details\n! colspan=\"1\"| Peak<br>chart<br>positions\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Comedy Albums|US<br>Comedy]]<br><ref>{{cite web|title=Billboard Chart Archive|url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/search/charts?f|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]| publisher =[[Prometheus Global Media]]|accessdate=May 17, 2015|format=To access, type \"Willam\" in the artist bar, the