[[prophylactic]], in combination with [[zinc]], [[vitamin A]], [[vitamin C]] and [[vitamin D]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.webmd.com/lung/news/20200409/chloroquine-zinc-tested-to-block-covid-infection |title=Chloroquine, Zinc Tested to Block COVID Infection |publisher=WebMD}}</ref>\n\n==Statistics==\n===By province===\n<div style=\"display: flex; width: 100%;\">{{2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic data/Turkey medical cases by province}}{{notelist-lr}}</div>\n\n===Data table===\n<!-- We need to turn this into a template at some point-->\n{|class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Date\n! colspan=\"3\" | Confirmed cases\n! colspan=\"2\" | Deaths\n! colspan=\"2\" | Recoveries\n! colspan=\"2\" | Severe cases\n! colspan=\"2\" | Number of tests\n|-\n!New\n!Total\n!Active{{efn|Active case number is calculated using total case number, deaths and recoveries, it is not announced by government}}\n!New\n!Total\n!New\n!Total\n!Intubated\n!ICU{{efn|Excluding intubated patients}}\n!New\n!Total\n|-\n|align=center|11 March 2020<ref name=\"Independent\"></ref>{{efn|\"-\" does not indicate \"0\", it means that no data is available}}\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|-\n|align=center|12 March 2020<ref name=\"13March\"></ref>\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|-\n|align=center|13 March 2020<ref name=\"13March\"></ref>\n|align=center|4\n|align=center|5\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|-\n|-\n|align=center|14 March 2020<ref name=\"14March\"></ref>\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|6 \n|align=center|-\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|-\n|align=ce