 The Voices)\" \u2013 [[Hall & Oates]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Cotter |first1=Jack |title=Hall & Oates Appreciation Day: \"Rich Girl\" |url=https://www.phillymag.com/news/2013/12/17/hall-oates-appreciation-day-rich-girl/ |website=Philly Mag |accessdate=26 July 2018 |date=December 17, 2013}}</ref>\n*\"I Hear Black\" \u2013 [[Overkill (band)|Overkill]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Songs About or Inspired by the Son of Sam |url=https://themusicalhype.com/songs-about-or-inspired-by-the-son-of-sam-playlist/7/ |website=The Musical Hype |accessdate=26 July 2018 |date=January 23, 2018}}</ref>\n*\"Hello From the Gutter\" \u2013 [[Overkill (band)|Overkill]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Cavuoto |first1=Robert |title=Interview with Bobby Blitz Ellsworth of Overkill: This is Our Calling |url=http://guitarinternational.com/2012/04/03/interview-with-bobby-blitz-ellsworth-of-overkill-this-is-our-calling/ |website=Guitar International |accessdate=26 July 2018}}</ref>\n*\"Hot Damn\" \u2013 [[Ivy Levan]]\n*\"Insane in the Brain\" \u2013 [[Cypress Hill]]<ref name=mentions>{{cite web |title=Songs About or Inspired by the Son of Sam |url=https://themusicalhype.com/songs-about-or-inspired-by-the-son-of-sam-playlist/12/ |website=The Musical Hype |accessdate=26 July 2018 |date=January 23, 2018}}</ref>\n*\"Jumping at Shadows\" \u2013 [[Benediction (band)|Benediction]]\n*\"Looking Down the Barrel of a Gun\" \u2013 [[Beastie Boys]]<ref name=mentions/>\n*\"Mr. 44\" \u2013 [[Electric Hellfire Club]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Songs About or Inspired by the Son of Sam |url=https://themusicalhype.com/songs-about-or-inspired-by-the-son-of-sam-playlist/8/ |website=The Musical Hype |accessdate=26 July 2018 |date=January 23, 2018}}</ref>\n*\"Reign In Blood\" \u2013 [[Necro (rapper)|Necro]]\n*\"(Sam), Son of Man\" \u2013 [[Marilyn Manson]] and The Spooky Kids\n*\"Stay Wide Awake\" \u2013 [[Eminem]]\n*\"Son of A Gun (David Berkowitz)\" \u2013 [[Church of Misery]]\n*\"Son of Sam\" - [[Chain Gang (band)|Chain Gang]]\n*\"Son o